OL,5,Cin Euros
OL,7,FPolice have warned of a potential rise
OL,8,Fin domestic abuse as England play
OL,9,FSerbia in their first game of the
OL,10,FEuropean football championship on
OL,11,FSunday.
OL,13,FThe National Police Chiefs' Council
OL,14,Fsaid a study from Lancaster University
OL,15,Ffound there was a 38% increase in
OL,16,Fdomestic violence incidents when
OL,17,FEngland lost a game between 2002 and
OL,18,F2010, and a 26% rise when they won.
