OL,3,CPolice warn of possible rise in
OL,4,Cdomestic abuse as England face Serbia
OL,5,Cin Euros
OL,7,FAssistant Commissioner Louisa Rolfe,
OL,8,FNPCC lead for domestic abuse, said she
OL,9,Fwanted to make victims of domestic
OL,10,Fabuse aware of the support available
OL,11,Fto them during the tournament and
OL,12,Fencouraged anyone who suffered abuse
OL,13,Fto report it to police immediately.
OL,15,FSpeaking to reporters at New Scotland
OL,16,FYard on Friday, she said: "It is an
OL,17,Fincredibly sad reality that football
OL,18,Ftournaments mean an increased risk of
OL,19,Fdomestic abuse for many victims across
OL,20,Fthe UK."
