OL,5,Cin Euros
OL,7,FMs Rolfe also cited findings by Sussex
OL,8,FPolice during the 2022 world cup,
OL,9,Fwhich showed that 999 calls relating
OL,10,Fto domestic abuse "doubled" during
OL,11,Fmatch days.
OL,13,FShe said: "I'm keen to ensure that
OL,14,Fvictims of domestic abuse are aware of
OL,15,Fthe support available to them,
OL,16,Fencouraged to report to police, and
OL,17,Fthat every perpetrator is held to
OL,18,Faccount.
