OL,5,Cin Euros
OL,7,F"Domestic abuse makes up 11% of all
OL,8,Fcalls to emergency services. It's more
OL,9,Fthan 30% of violent incidents reported
OL,10,Fto the police.
OL,12,F"Domestic abuse is not a gendered
OL,13,Fcrime, but women are
OL,14,Fdisproportionately victims."
OL,16,FTeresa Parker, head of media at the
OL,17,Fcharity Women's Aid, said that women
OL,18,Fand their children staying at refuges
OL,19,Fwould not want to have the TV on
OL,20,Fduring England games because of their
OL,21,Fpast experiences.
