OL,5,Cin Euros
OL,7,FMs Parker said: "We were being told by
OL,8,Fwomen in refuges across the country
OL,9,Fthat they would not have the TV on
OL,10,Fduring major tournaments. For so many
OL,11,Ffamilies it triggers the feeling that
OL,12,Fsomething worse might happen.
OL,14,F"I spoke to three women whose partners
OL,15,Flove football and were abusive in long-
OL,16,Fterm relationships. Football was a
OL,17,Ftrigger."
