OL,7,FAsked what measures the police plan to
OL,8,Fuse during the tournament to ensure
OL,9,Fwomen's safety, Ms Rolfe said: "We
OL,10,Fwant to work closely with charities to
OL,11,Fmake sure victims are aware that they
OL,12,Fare able to come forward.
OL,14,F"We want to work out who the abusers
OL,15,Fare that we want to manage and we'll
OL,16,Fbe using domestic violence protection
OL,17,Forders and restraint orders to do so
OL,18,Fthroughout the tournament.
