OL,7,F"Sussex Police are organising joint
OL,8,Fpatrols, where officers responding to
OL,9,Fincidents will have an independent
OL,10,Fdomestic violence advocate with them
OL,11,Fso that the victim has many options
OL,12,Favailable to them."
OL,14,FMs Parker added: "I feel passionately
OL,15,Fthat football can do good. We are
OL,16,Fengaging with football clubs and
OL,17,Forganisations, like Fulham, where we
OL,18,Fdo training and awareness.
OL,20,F"The more we can work together the
OL,21,Fbetter."
