OL,7,FMs Rolfe said: "The vast majority of
OL,8,Fmen who love football would never
OL,9,Fdream of abusing their partner. But we
OL,10,Fneed their help in calling out those
OL,11,Fwho would. We need their help in
OL,12,Fchallenging those who might."
OL,14,FSeparately, women's aid charity Solace
OL,15,Fand the National Centre for Domestic
OL,16,FViolence, have created an alternative
OL,17,FEngland kit ` "Shirt 38" ` to raise
OL,18,Fawareness of the support available to
OL,19,Fanyone experiencing domestic abuse as
OL,20,Fpart of their "No More Injury Time"
OL,21,Fcampaign ahead of the Euros.
